fm: void CTelBLLConverter::ConvertData(const void* srcData, const UI_32 srcDataSize, void* dstData, const UI_32 dstDataSize) { 	//BTSRV_DEBUG_LOG(ZONE_FUNC, __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, "+"); 	 	if (NULL == srcData) 	{ 		//BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_ERR, __FUNCTION__, "Err: Parameter(srcData) NULL"); 		return; 	} 	 	if (NULL == dstData) 	{ 		//BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_ERR, __FUNCTION__, "Err: Parameter(dstData) NULL"); 		return; 	} 	 	(void)memset(dstData, 0x00, dstDataSize); 	if (dstDataSize > srcDataSize) 	{ 		(void)memcpy(dstData, srcData, srcDataSize); 	} 	else 	{ 		(void)memcpy(dstData, srcData, dstDataSize); 	} 	 	//BTSRV_DEBUG_LOG(ZONE_FUNC, __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, "-"); }

fm: EPasStatus CTelBLLConverter::ConvertReturnCode(const EBTSRV_TelBLLReturnCode returnCode) { 	//BTSRV_DEBUG_LOG(ZONE_FUNC, __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, "+"); 	 	struct ConvTable { 		EBTSRV_TelBLLReturnCode src; 		EPasStatus dst; 	};     const ConvTable tbl[] = {         { eBTSRV_TelBLLReturnCode_SUCCESS, ePasStatusOK   },         { eBTSRV_TelBLLReturnCode_FAILURE, ePasStatusFail },     }; 	 	EPasStatus ret = ePasStatusFail; 	 	for (UI_32 i = 0; i < _countof(tbl); i++) 	{ 		if (tbl[i].src == returnCode) 		{ 			ret = tbl[i].dst; 			break; 		} 	} 	 	//BTSRV_DEBUG_LOG(ZONE_FUNC, __PRETTY_FUNCTION__, "-"); 	 	return ret; }
